<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Alpha leh Omega</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Amah a kiengu-ah um intin,
 Amauhaw chu a mite hi ta nau;
 Pathien ngei chun umpih intin,
 A mit u a mitthi chu thiek hul tan a.

[V2]
 Dangchak tapohte kiengah,
 Hinna tuikhuka tui,
 A thawnin na pieng ka,
 Aw, thagau dangchakte chun va dawn u hen.

[V3]
 2. Thihna umkit nawn thei ta puona,
 Lungkham naubang kahna natnate le;
 Um kit nawn thei ding ei ta puoi
 Thil masahaw cheng le a beizo tau hi.

[V4]
 3. &quot; Ngaitie thil bangkim ka siem thak tai,
 Zikin, ziethu hi a ginchak um hi&quot;
 Chun ka kawmah a hung tung tai,
 &quot;Kei Alpha leh Omega a Bul leh Tawp.

[V5]
 4. A Masapen leh a Nunungpen,
 Hinna Thing chungah thu a nei thei ui;
 Khuoa a lut theihna diu a,
 Kisuthiengtho haw chu a nau vak tana.</lyrics>
<author>Siamliana</author>
<hymn_number>196</hymn_number>
</song>